# NAME: Game
# AUTHOR: steak
# TYPE: Quantumult X Filter
# DESCRIPTION: Steam / Epic / PlayStation / Nintendo / Battle.net / Ubisoft / EA / Xbox 等游戏平台分流规则
# SOURCE: Split from GlobalServices.list
# UPDATED: 2026-05-11
#
# ================================
# 使用说明
# ================================
# 1. 文件名：Game.list
# 2. 适用于：Quantumult X [filter_remote]
# 3. 策略组名称：游戏平台
# 4. 本文件由原 GlobalServices.list 拆分，便于后续单独维护
# 5. IP-CIDR / IP6-CIDR 已追加 no-resolve
#
# QX 远程订阅示例：
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/reverie1988/QX/refs/heads/main/Rules/Game.list, tag=Game, force-policy=游戏平台, update-interval=172800, opt-parser=false, enabled=true
#
# ================================
# 规则统计
# ================================
# HOST: 8
# HOST-SUFFIX: 61
# HOST-KEYWORD: 7
# USER-AGENT: 0
# IP-CIDR: 0
# IP6-CIDR: 0
# IP-ASN: 0
# TOTAL: 76
#
# ================================
# 规则内容
# ================================
# 游戏平台
# ================================

